1776611545680012	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy0go		item.create	bn-31v8	{"description":"tests/action_workflow_dst.rs:1253 fails with an assertion in the deterministic simulation test. Reproduces on clean main (HEAD = 92027a2 at v0.59.3) as well as with bn-2538's test-helper fix applied. Unrelated to bn-3o8k (status fast path) or bn-2538 (test setup isolation).\n\nCommand: cargo test --release --test action_workflow_dst dst_action_sequences_preserve_contracts\n\nSymptom: test panicked at tests/action_workflow_dst.rs:1253:5. Ran for ~42s before failing.\n\nLooks like it may be a DST (deterministic simulation) seed issue — needs investigation to determine if it's a real invariant break or a flaky seed / platform difference.","kind":"task","title":"test(dst): dst_action_sequences_preserve_contracts failing on main"}	blake3:BD5Zr0dr9wppxoZaT6gju-JqSRBw-vKdJPIWNhZxKvc
